::Killfest/Demise/Scyther/Greven/EndBringer::

Killfest freezes in his tracks, his scanners picking something up.

"A ship is landing on the planet," he informs Darkfate, "My team will 
check it out."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
With a silent order from Killfest, Demise, Scyther, Greven, and 
EndBringer walk out of the cave, running off toward the new ship's 
location.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> Blazing overhead, the starcruiser passes by northern Africa like a 
> meteor but not quite. 
> [Inside] "Stunicons: we are approaching our intended destination, 
> everyone in place. Motormaster, we are ready to land, ETA 3 
> minutes and counting."
> "Drag Strip, make sure the landing gear is out. No mistakes!" 
> rumbles one of the passengers.
> The craft manages to squeeze into a little bay along the southern 
> most inside part of mid-eastern futur Canada.
